name: What Does Your Startup Do?
tag_list: animation, custom-animation, custom-video, intro-videos, animated-video, overview-videos, explainers, production-company, motion-graphics, explanation, explainer-video, screencast-video, marketing, animation-studio, demo-videos
overview:
What Does Your Startup Do helps startups explain what they do and improve site conversions by creating original animated explainer videos.

WDYSD works with their clients to make videos at prices startups can afford. If you are looking for someone to produce a video, WDYSD will take your video from concept through animation. If your startup is looking to save money on your video, the WDYSD team will work with your startup’s in-house talent (graphic design, copywriting, etc) to make the video even more affordable.

Portfolio: http://www.wdysd.com/portfolio.html
